sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Sidecar as Istio Sidecar<br/>mTLS STRICT
    participant Server as AutoGluon Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Storage as Object Storage<br/>S3/GCS/Azure/HF<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Server,Storage: Flow 1: Model Loading at Startup
        Server->>Storage: HTTPS GET model artifacts<br/>Auth: IAM / Bearer / SA
        Storage-->>Server: Model files downloaded to local disk
        Note over Server: Auto-detect predictor type:<br/>Try TimeSeriesPredictor first,<br/>fallback to TabularPredictor
        Note over Server: Validate version compatibility<br/>(patch-level mismatch allowed)
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,Server: Flow 2: Tabular Inference (v1 REST)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / mTLS
        Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward request<br/>mTLS
        Sidecar->>Server: HTTP POST :8080<br/>PeerAuthentication STRICT
        Note over Server: Parse JSON → pandas DataFrame<br/>TabularPredictor.predict()
        Server-->>Sidecar: JSON predictions response
        Sidecar-->>Gateway: mTLS
        Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,Server: Flow 2b: Tabular Inference (v2 Tensor)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / mTLS
        Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward request<br/>mTLS
        Sidecar->>Server: HTTP POST :8080<br/>PeerAuthentication STRICT
        Note over Server: Parse InferRequest tensors<br/>→ map feature names → DataFrame<br/>TabularPredictor.predict()
        Server-->>Sidecar: InferResponse with tensors
        Sidecar-->>Gateway: mTLS
        Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over Client,Server: Flow 3: Time Series Inference (v1 REST only)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / mTLS
        Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward request<br/>mTLS
        Sidecar->>Server: HTTP POST :8080<br/>PeerAuthentication STRICT
        Note over Server: Parse JSON → TimeSeriesDataFrame<br/>TimeSeriesPredictor.predict()<br/>Returns mean + quantile forecasts
        Server-->>Sidecar: JSON forecast response
        Sidecar-->>Gateway: mTLS
        Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS JSON Response
    end
